<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="annoy-vt">annoy <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'nɔɪ/    美 /ə'nɔɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>使恼怒；使烦恼；使生气</strong></h4>
<p>to make sb feel slightly angry and unhappy：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her cold voice really annoyed me.
她冷冰冰的声音真让我恼火。</p><footer>2016 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It really annoys me when I see people dropping litter.
看到别人乱丢垃圾我真的很生气。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>annoying /ə'nɔɪɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>